{
  "stem": "8191.1",
  "chunk_idx": 0,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Jacques Rosenthal.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "J-A-C-Q-U-E-S R-O-S-E-N-T-H-A-L.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Before, it was J-A-K-U-B.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In that time when I was born, it was Russia, in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "March the 24th, 1911.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 3,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, very little I can tell you.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I only remember when we came back to Warsaw, end of the-- that was October or November 1917.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We came back after the, the revolution.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so I remember only from 18-- from 1918 till '21 till we left Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "In that time, I remember [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the war was still on with Russia and Germany.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And the soldier-- we used to live in a street close to the station-- that we saw daily coming wounded soldiers and going back-- new soldiers to the front and my house.",
      "word_count": 32
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "In the house that we were living in at that time, there was a bakery.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so they baked bread, and they brought it up to the third floor where we used to live.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And my father and mother, who could give a hand, used to throw the bread to the-- to the people that were walking to the station-- soldiers.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And then I remember the Declaration-- Balfour Declarations in 1919.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had an uncle that was one of the pioneers in Zionism.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was Nachum Sokolov.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "In all of the organization for the big event after we had the declaration from Great Britain was a preparation for making our house.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] And in 1919, I was seven, eight years old.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "They said that I cannot go to the celebration.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I didn't say anything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Maybe a few days before they tell me this-- you'll have to stay home.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But the day of the celebration, I cried.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And Nachum Sokolov was an uncle to my mother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he asked, why is he crying?",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
